snippet.title: One Day Builds: Instagram Automation Using Python
snippet.description:
One Day Builds: Instagram Automation Using Python

In this one day build I automate the process of posting to instagram using a python script. Allowing me to do more effective task batching for instagram. I really enjoyed it, I hope you do too :)

My Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/kallehallden/

Tim Ferris Podcast: 
https://tim.blog/2019/06/27/josh-waitzkin/

GITHUB: https://github.com/KalleHallden/InstaAutomator
